body: So I don't really have anywhere else to put this,since I don't have a reddit account nor am I in a Splatoon-related discord server. But as of yesterday,March 5th 2019. I ShotgunBucker (SPOILERS AHEAD) had defeated Inner Agent 3. It only took me about 10 hours (6 from a few months ago,+4 from yesterday.) but HOLY SHIT that feeling of satisfaction after beating him (I want with Male 3 & Female 8) was one of the best feelings i've had all-year. Phase 5 is what scared me the most,because if the sudden "I have an extra Splashdown bitch",I beat him just as he had it. Needless to say,I wanted to show-off just a bit.

Really enjoy this hentai but since I can't read this my guess is that everyone heard them have intense sex with that machine which caused her to be embarrassed for the rest of her life. I'll give a plus on how adorable they are together at the end which gives me warmth however that inkling really knows on how the fuck a good body up.
Lol as soon as I saw this I was like oh boy
There's no english version....I'm disappointed since the art is so good.
